fs.fibu2.data.format
Class Fsfibu2DateFormats

java.lang.Object
  fs.fibu2.data.format.Fsfibu2DateFormats

public class Fsfibu2DateFormats
extends java.lang.Object

This class summarizes some static strings specifying date format patterns. There is a method for retrieving the associated SimpleDateFormat and for parsing a GregorianCalendar object from a string for each format.

Author:
Simon Hampe

public static final java.lang.String entryDateFormat
